  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO AMEND SECTION 25-7-21, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO RAISE THE RATE TO $3.00 FOR EACH SEPARATE PUBLICATION ADVERTISING LANDS FOR SALES TAXES; TO PROVIDE THAT THE RATE SHALL INCREASE EACH YEAR STARTING JULY 1, 2027, AT A RATE COMPARABLE TO THE CONSUMER PRICE INDEX; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
